<h2>6. Restoring Subscriptions</h2>
<p>If you reinstall Poem Ai or switch devices, you can use the "Restore Purchase" option in the app settings. This allows you to regain access to previously purchased subscriptions without being charged again. Restoring is required to ensure users retain access to paid features across devices and installations.</p>

